The paper deals with game theory and mechanism design, specifically in the context of congestion games. Therefore, cs.GT (Game Theory) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves multi-agent systems and coordination, which falls under cs.MA (Multiagent Systems). The use of a mediator and the analysis of equilibria involve algorithms and data structures, which could be classified under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also involves learning and optimization, which could be classified under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
